    "The spark will ignite the flammable liquid……Figure 1: Example of Jailbreak Attack on MiniGPT-4 [29].The proposed Universal Master key (UMK) helps arbitrary harmful queries bypass alignment constraints.Specifically, we employ white-box attacks to identify a multimodal adversarial example capable of jailbreaking VLMs, which we refer to as the Universal Master Key (UMK).",
